				</div>

				<div>
					<p class="date">2019</p>
					<div class="row">
						<div class="blog">
							<li class="title">
								<a href="/blogs/into_unknown"
									>Into The Unknown: The Truth About the Universe</a
								>
							</li>
							<p class="word">
								The universe itself is billions of years old, while the earliest
								human only first appeared a couple of million years ago on this
								tiny, insignificant spec of dust in this ever-expanding,
								never-ending universe which in turn is marching through its own
								life. But, with the advent of the more evolved human, came
